"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"A large crowd gathered outside a church in Moscow for the funeral of Alexei Navalny, a prominent opposition leader in Russia. Only a few people were allowed to attend the service, which was heavily guarded by police.\",            \"english_title\": \"Death of Alexei Navalny\",            \"translated_version\": \"Mucha gente se reuni\u00f3 afuera de una iglesia en Mosc\u00fa para el funeral de Alexei Navalny, un l\u00edder opositor importante en Rusia. Solo unas pocas personas pudieron asistir al servicio, que estaba fuertemente custodiado por la polic\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muerte de Alexei Navalny\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Elon Musk filed a lawsuit against OpenAI, an artificial-intelligence firm he helped establish, and its chief executive, Sam Altman. Musk claimed that the company has strayed from its original goal of benefiting humanity.\",            \"english_title\": \"Elon Musk Sues OpenAI\",            \"translated_version\": \"Elon Musk present\u00f3 una demanda contra OpenAI, una empresa de inteligencia artificial que ayud\u00f3 a establecer, y su director ejecutivo, Sam Altman. Musk afirm\u00f3 que la empresa se ha alejado de su objetivo original de beneficiar a la humanidad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Elon Musk demanda a OpenAI\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Authorities in Gaza reported that Israeli soldiers shot and killed over 100 Palestinians and injured many more near aid trucks. Conflicting reports suggest that a stampede may have caused most of the deaths. President Joe Biden mentioned that this incident could complicate ceasefire talks.\",            \"english_title\": \"Violence in Gaza\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las autoridades en Gaza informaron que soldados israel\u00edes dispararon y mataron a m\u00e1s de 100 palestinos e hirieron a muchos m\u00e1s cerca de camiones de ayuda. Informes contradictorios sugieren que una estampida podr\u00eda haber causado la mayor\u00eda de las muertes. El presidente Joe Biden mencion\u00f3 que este incidente podr\u00eda complicar las conversaciones de alto el fuego.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Violencia en Gaza\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"George Galloway, a far-left politician, won a by-election in Rochdale by overturning a large Labour majority. His campaign focused on criticizing Labour's stance on the war in Gaza and its failure to condemn Israel.\",            \"english_title\": \"George Galloway Wins By-Election\",            \"translated_version\": \"George Galloway, un pol\u00edtico de extrema izquierda, gan\u00f3 una elecci\u00f3n parcial en Rochdale al revertir una gran mayor\u00eda laborista. Su campa\u00f1a se centr\u00f3 en criticar la postura del Partido Laborista sobre la guerra en Gaza y su fracaso en condenar a Israel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"George Galloway gana elecci\u00f3n parcial\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A new study published in Lancet revealed that over 1 billion people were obese in 2022. The study highlighted a significant increase in obesity rates among adults and children since 1990, with higher rates in low- and middle-income countries.\",            \"english_title\": \"Global Obesity Rates\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un nuevo estudio publicado en Lancet revel\u00f3 que m\u00e1s de 1 mil millones de personas ten\u00edan obesidad en 2022. El estudio destac\u00f3 un aumento significativo en las tasas de obesidad entre adultos y ni\u00f1os desde 1990, con tasas m\u00e1s altas en pa\u00edses de ingresos bajos y medios.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tasas globales de obesidad\"        }    ]}"